{"tid":2014341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌指限制社交距離措施未需即時收緊但一定不能放寬","createTime":"2020-05-13T03:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T03:47:29.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0efe5613e870fdaa7feca1595f34b4916f6964","tid":2014341,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"許樹昌指限制社交距離措施未需即時收緊但一定不能放寬<br />\n2020-05-13 HKT 11:20<br />\n<br />\n消息指，一名66歲女子兩次病毒測試結果均呈陽性，很大機會被列為新一宗本地確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n政府專家顧問之一、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌說，若消息屬實，現時限制社交距離的措施未必需要即時收緊，但一定不能放寬，例如可以維持酒樓每枱最多坐8人，但在人多的地方必須戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌說，出現零星確診個案是預計之內，但現在最大問題是找不到感染源頭，不排除是港人回港完成家居隔離後才發病。<br />\n<br />\n被問到目前是否不適宜放寬邊境檢疫措施，許樹昌認為，要視乎未來幾個星期有沒有來歷不明的感染個案和群組感染，才能夠下定論。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525859-20200513.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525859-20200513.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=31319b10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525859-20200513.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9da17d28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525859-20200513.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唉&hellip;&hellip;我好想有得唱k同埋去老蘭聽live band<br />\n睇黎希望幻滅了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e056cdadd2207d54450ca7367adef3acf14075ea","tid":2014341,"uid":187957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但現在最大問題是找不到感染源頭</span><br />\n你阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bcd7f654f4f675cc7faccf5353b76efcb851f3","tid":2014341,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03